      <title>欧洲央行行长施纳贝尔认为进一步降息的空间有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行需要警惕过度降息，因为借贷成本已经接近不再抑制经济的水平，降息可能会适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ecb-rate-cuts-schnabel-sees-only-limited-room-for-further-reductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
